{
  "name": "voice",
  "display_name": "Voice Tools",
  "description": "Voice pipeline controls (push-to-talk, wake word, TTS). Placeholder — the pipeline lives in services/api/athena_api/voice/; these tools activate once STT/TTS providers are installed (see docs/VOICE.md).",
